WEBVTT

00:00:00.831 --> 00:00:04.277
The technology likely to have
the greatest impact

00:00:04.301 --> 00:00:06.047
on the next few decades

00:00:06.071 --> 00:00:07.323
has arrived.

00:00:07.744 --> 00:00:10.241
And it's not social media.

00:00:10.265 --> 00:00:11.662
It's not big data.

00:00:11.686 --> 00:00:13.193
It's not robotics.

00:00:13.217 --> 00:00:14.700
It's not even AI.

00:00:15.033 --> 00:00:17.399
You'll be surprised to learn

00:00:17.423 --> 00:00:22.135
that it's the underlying technology
of digital currencies like Bitcoin.

00:00:22.159 --> 00:00:25.560
It's called the blockchain. Blockchain.

00:00:26.337 --> 00:00:29.173
Now, it's not the most sonorous
word in the world,